Interface Resource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Asset, Described, DescribedSemantically, DigitalContent, ManagedEntity
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AppResource, AudioResource, DataResource, ImageResource, SoftwareResource, TextResource, VideoResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AppResourceImpl, AudioResourceImpl, DataResourceImpl, ImageResourceImpl, ResourceImpl, SoftwareResourceImpl, TextResourceImpl, VideoResourceImpl

    public interface Resource
extends Asset, DigitalContent, DescribedSemantically, ManagedEntity
    "Resource"@en "Resource is a single digital content or a coherent set of digital contents. Resource content is formalized in Representations and optionally materialized as Artifacts. The Resource\'s content is exposed via defined Interfaces at various protocol Endpoints."@en
